 with the state-of-the-art on four\ndatasets, namely, MNIST, CIFAR10, CIFAR100 and ImageNet to establish a new\nbaseline in two different settings.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 11 Oct 2022 20:20:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-13"}
