it. In this scheme, the effect of all the physical\nscattering mechanisms is lumped into one energy uncertainty or scattering rate\nparameter to include in the device's contact self-energy interaction term bound\nby the upper limit of Heisenberg uncertainty for the interacting quantum\ncharged particles.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 11 Oct 2022 23:24:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-13"}
