ties of typical micro-size objects, such as\natmospheric particulates and living cells, for a wide range of applications in\ne.g., acoustic sensing, gravimetry, and inertial navigation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 12 Oct 2022 12:46:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-01"}
