q3$. Our findings pave the way\nto the exploration of interacting quantum Hall systems in 4D, from the\ninvestigation of strongly-correlated liquids to the simulation of high-energy\nmodels in link with quantum gravity and Yang-Mills field theory.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 12 Oct 2022 15:41:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-13"}
