vorable properties in each group that could play a role in\nobtaining admissible solutions. Finally, we find the $\\Theta$-series associated\nwith levels $p = 2,3,5,7$ and the corresponding lattice data of Kissing numbers\nand lattice radii for each case. We find that the Fricke $\\Theta$-series of\nlevel $p = 2$ has distinctive ties to the odd Leech lattice in $24$-dimensions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 12 Oct 2022 10:27:08 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 17 Oct 2022 19:48:09 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 23 Oct 2022 00:51:12 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 23 Feb 2023 22:21:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-27"}
